  "title": "Locum Staff Nurse (UP TO $32/HR) #HJOT",
  "description": "<p><br />We are hiring Locum SN to be outsourced to our clients from reputable healthcare organizations.</p><p>Apply now!<br /></p><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Perform vital signs monitoring, and assist with procedures.</li><li>Assist doctors during ward rounds, procedures</li><li>Carry out bedside nursing duties</li><li>Ensure patient comfort and safety, and serve prescribed medications.</li><li>Monitor patients’ conditions, identify changes, and escalate promptly</li><li>Maintain infection control and safety standards within the ward environment.</li><li>Ad-hoc duties</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Able to work 3 to 4 days a week </li><li>Valid BCLS and SNB</li><li><strong>Min 1 year of inpatient experience</strong></li><li>full immunization against MMR (2 doses), TDAP (within last 10 years), COVID (3 doses)</li></ul><p>All Interested candidates are invited to email your resume in MS Word format to:</p><p>healthscience@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Please include your full working experience, education background, notice period, expected salary.</p><p>Krislyn Chng</p><p>Outsourcing Team</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p>We regret to inform that only suitable candidates will be shortlisted for an interview.</p><p><br /></p>",
